node.text: We've got a brand new song coming your way this Friday! Who do y'all think is singing on this one with me?👇 #IfIDidntLoveYou

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jason Aldean on July 18, 2021 tagging @tullykennedy, @kurtallison, and @tpm_nashville. May be an image of 1 person, playing a musical instrument and standing.

node.text: Thank you for taking “Blame it on You” to #1 this week. This one feels especially sweet because it was written by 2 guys that have been with me for over 20 years. It’s our 25th number 1 together but the first one they have written that I sang on to get there. Thanks to everybody who had a part in it. 🤙🏼 #tripleplaymusic

node.text: Proud to announce that my new publishing company Triple Play Music I founded with my boys @tullykennedy and @kurtallison  has partnered up with Play It Again Music Groups new company Double Down music in a new joint venture. We have Big Plans for 2021!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Jason Aldean on July 11, 2021 tagging @tullykennedy, @justinmrusek, and @kurtallison. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and crowd.

node.text: Such a rush last nite playing Country Concert in Ohio. Feels good to finally be back in saddle! 2021 is about to be 🔥. See y’all next weekend at @fasterhorsesfestival 🤘🏼

node.text: Me and lil man jammin to @hardy today before our show. I think he has the music bug! Get ready for Memphis Aldean in a few years people!!! 🤟🏼

node.text: Vegas! Excited to see y'all at Park Theater at @ParkMGM for three nights THIS December 9, 10 & 11. Tickets are on sale NOW! Link in bio.

node.text: Happy Father’s Day to my Pops @bigdawg1953 One of the coolest and funniest guys I know. Love you dad. Also, here’s to all the other dads, bonus dads and grandads out there. 🍻 #happyfathersday
